分地区有暴雨或大暴雨（100—150 毫米）。 防御指南： 1. 政府及相关部门按照职责做好防台风抢险应急工作。 2. 相关水域水上作业和过往船舶应当回港避风，加固港口设施，防止船舶走锚、搁浅和碰撞。 3. 停止室内外大型集会和高空等户外危险作业。 「梅花」向北偏西方向移动，江浙沪局地有暴雨或大暴雨 _ 绿政公署 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-340b9ab013f388dd60a62922a2db7e7b_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/553075923"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIlOr104WcyItFEAMaCDg1MTg5MzU1II/7+ZgGMAE4K0Avcgk1NTMwNzU5MjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1662999013.74259", "card_id": "Q_552680419", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价周深的新歌《花开忘忧》？听了歌，你想起谁了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "你是否曾想过， 每当说一声再见，就会开启一个新的世界。 有一个平行时空，让所有遗憾变得圆满"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-84e61e0f4953975ae1830036780cb345_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/552680419"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlOr104WcyItFEAMaCDg1MTAxMTQyIIbd7ZgGMAc4kAFAMHIJNTUyNjgwNDE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1662999013.7434742", "card_id": "Q_550158172", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 83}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《原神》须弥森林书和稻妻神樱大祓系列任务？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2e739973bd143566a87c6492c36416ee_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/550158172"}}, 